      <p>In relation to this process, that means to stick with it! I recall that one of my clients was stuck and unable to even call in her first dollar &ndash; by sitting with her on her beliefs and getting her into alignment with them, she ended up receiving 10,000 within a week or two for a tax return that she had not even filed yet!</p>
