      <h5 class="header">THE MIND JUST FOLLOWS PROTOCOLS</h5>
      <p>The mind is not set up to lie to itself, it is simply following protocols that have been fed to it by prior inputs. By giving it evidence via your inputs and from that space in your mind&rsquo;s eye, seeing the intention as a done thing, you create an open path to manifesting your intention.</p>
